<paragraph blockId="12.[160,1156,141,548]" pageId="12" pageNumber="877">
Described by 
<bibRefCitation author="Kielland J" box="[315,475,178,202]" pageId="12" pageNumber="877" refId="ref22372" refString="Kielland J. 1990. Butterflies of Tanzania. Melbourne: Hill House." type="book" year="1990">Kielland (1990</bibRefCitation>
, p. 84) as 
<emphasis box="[590,595,178,202]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="877">‘</emphasis>
very common in woodland and savanna from sea level to 
<quantity box="[257,344,212,236]" metricMagnitude="3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.15" pageId="12" pageNumber="877" unit="m" value="2150.0">2150 m</quantity>
... throughout the country in suitable habitats 
<emphasis box="[894,899,212,236]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="877">’</emphasis>
. In contrast, noted as 
<emphasis box="[160,166,247,271]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="877">‘</emphasis>
rare 
<emphasis box="[209,215,247,271]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="877">’</emphasis>
during the dry season only at Lake 
<collectingRegion box="[637,733,247,271]" country="Tanzania" name="Manyara" pageId="12" pageNumber="877">Manyara</collectingRegion>
National Park (
<bibRefCitation author="Moehlman PD &amp; Liseki SD" pageId="12" pageNumber="877" refId="ref22985" refString="Moehlman PD, Liseki SD. 2003. A guide to the butterflies of Tarangire National Park and Lake Manyara National Park. Gland: WWF." type="book" year="2003">Moehlman and Liseki 2003</bibRefCitation>
). 
<materialsCitation ID-GBIF-Occurrence="2832026333" collectionCode="OUMNH" location="Taveta" pageId="12" pageNumber="877" specimenCount="10" specimenCount-male="10">
This butterfly is included here as a member of the lower slopes fauna on the basis of 
<specimenCount box="[193,296,316,340]" pageId="12" pageNumber="877" type="male">10 males</specimenCount>
in 
<collectionCode box="[338,430,316,340]" pageId="12" pageNumber="877">OUMNH</collectionCode>
from 
<location LSID="urn:lsid:plazi:treatment:03E687FCFFABFF8F4983FB63FC96FD95:8E906031FFACFF8F49FCFEDFFDFCFEE5" box="[504,578,316,340]" name="Taveta" pageId="12" pageNumber="877">Taveta</location>
collected at c
</materialsCitation>
. 
<materialsCitation ID-GBIF-Occurrence="2832026325" collectingDate="1937-01" collectionCode="BMNH" collectorName="F. J. Jackson" elevation="762" location="Marangu" municipality="Cooper" pageId="12" pageNumber="877" specimenCount="1" stateProvince="Kilimanjaro">
<quantity box="[761,843,316,340]" metricMagnitude="2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="7.62" pageId="12" pageNumber="877" unit="ft" value="2500.0">
<elevation box="[761,843,316,340]" metricMagnitude="2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="7.62" pageId="12" pageNumber="877" unit="ft" value="2500.0">2500 ft</elevation>
